To complete the subtask "Agree to the License Agreement", the mouse needs to be moved to the check box next to the agreement, and then click the left button to select the check box. The following is the JSON instruction to complete this action:```json
[
    {"action_type": "MouseAction", "mouse_action_type": "click", "mouse_button": "left", "mouse_position": {"width": 339, "height": 471}}
]
```This action assumes that the position of the check box "I have read and agreed to Terms and Privacy Policy" is about 500 pixels wide and 525 pixels high on the screen. Please adjust the value according to the actual screen layout.
